data.title: Sr. Software Engineer
data.meta_description: Submit your resume for the C++ Software Engineer jobs at Flexsin.
data.text:
Job Description:

We are hiring Qliksense consultants with a minimum of 5 Yrs. experience. Strong knowledge of QlikView and Qlik Sense, including data modeling and scripting. Proficiency in data visualization, dashboards, and report development.

Responsibilities:

Excellent SQL skills and familiarity with data warehouses and data sources.

Strong problem-solving and analytical skills.

Good communication and interpersonal skills

Work closely with clients to gather and analyze their data analytics requirements.

Design, develop, and implement data visualization solutions using QlikView and Qlik Sense.

Create interactive and user-friendly dashboards, reports, and data visualizations.

Optimize Qlik applications for performance, scalability, and user experience.

Customize and extend Qlik solutions through scripting and expressions.

Perform data modeling and data transformation to support analytical needs.

Collaborate with stakeholders to define KPIs and data analytics best practices.

Provide technical expertise and guidance to clients on Qlik product capabilities.

Conduct training sessions and knowledge transfer to end-users and client teams.

Stay up to date with the latest Qlik technologies and best practices.

Ability to work independently and as part of a team

Qualification:

Strong knowledge of QlikView and Qlik Sense, including data modeling and scripting.

Proficiency in data visualization, dashboards, and report development.

Excellent SQL skills and familiarity with data warehouses and data sources.

Strong problem-solving and analytical skills.

Good communication and interpersonal skills.

Ability to work independently and as part of a team
